snippet.title: Cosmic Ark (1982) Imagic
snippet.description: Cosmic Ark is an Atari 2600 game designed by Rob Fulop and published by Imagic in 1982. Fulop did the port of Missile Command for the 2600. Later he would design the controversial game Night Trap. Following Night Trap he create the Dogz and Catz games.
